  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/d134605b77f58b7e7695f3306f5a5dc0.poster.avif?t=1750935343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/d134605b77f58b7e7695f3306f5a5dc0.webm?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/d134605b77f58b7e7695f3306f5a5dc0.mp4?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play</strong> video pinball, <strong>relax</strong> in vaporwave environments and enjoy an <strong>anti-stress digital holiday</strong>.<br><strong><i>This is not pinball simulation but pinball stimulation.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 unlockable tables.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 layers per table.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >unlock everything in a few hours.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play endless to beat your own high score.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bespoke Vaporwave soundtrack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/48b5f990376149da40d23e86afdde56d.poster.avif?t=1750935343\" width=600 height=34 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/48b5f990376149da40d23e86afdde56d.webm?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/48b5f990376149da40d23e86afdde56d.mp4?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover new layers</strong> on each table and dive deeper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/7ac4daa9f9df5b36c5c6fc7207624193.poster.avif?t=1750935343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/7ac4daa9f9df5b36c5c6fc7207624193.webm?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/7ac4daa9f9df5b36c5c6fc7207624193.mp4?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bounce your way to beat your own high score or <strong>simply chill in a liminal dream</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/7ff79239d86232c2d38fe572d018291e.poster.avif?t=1750935343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/7ff79239d86232c2d38fe572d018291e.webm?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/7ff79239d86232c2d38fe572d018291e.mp4?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed to play for <strong>a few minutes</strong> or <strong>a</strong> <strong>few hours</strong>, at a time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/ac33ecf336911f2b30dcaf51bac9d0bf.poster.avif?t=1750935343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/ac33ecf336911f2b30dcaf51bac9d0bf.webm?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/ac33ecf336911f2b30dcaf51bac9d0bf.mp4?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stimulation </strong>not simulation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/a2de7e9ad766f35c6b41dc041fa186f2.poster.avif?t=1750935343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/a2de7e9ad766f35c6b41dc041fa186f2.webm?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/a2de7e9ad766f35c6b41dc041fa186f2.mp4?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Things you can <strong>only do in video pinball.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/410432e61360d497fb87fbc1b6af9ff9.poster.avif?t=1750935343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/410432e61360d497fb87fbc1b6af9ff9.webm?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/410432e61360d497fb87fbc1b6af9ff9.mp4?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes things <strong>get a bit weird.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/66b3e397948debf91408e92c1eb7c86e.poster.avif?t=1750935343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/66b3e397948debf91408e92c1eb7c86e.webm?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/66b3e397948debf91408e92c1eb7c86e.mp4?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But <strong>always fun.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/f7dcaead46868cd4bd97748321d948c2.poster.avif?t=1750935343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/f7dcaead46868cd4bd97748321d948c2.webm?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465930/extras/f7dcaead46868cd4bd97748321d948c2.mp4?t=1750935343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring an <strong>original</strong> <strong>Vaporwave Soundtrack. </strong><br><br><br><strong></strong><br> </p>",
